00:31:21.900 --> 00:31:24.660
that our greatest need is redemption.

00:31:25.060 --> 00:31:26.060
Amen.

00:31:26.060 --> 00:31:27.460
It's redemption.

00:31:27.460 --> 00:31:28.300
To be saved.

00:31:28.300 --> 00:31:31.700
We sang this morning a couple of songs about being saved.

00:31:31.700 --> 00:31:35.500
Christ receiveth sinful men whosoever will may come.

00:31:35.500 --> 00:31:39.100
You begin to think about the greatest need of humanity.

00:31:39.100 --> 00:31:41.820
The greatest need of humanity is not finances.

00:31:41.820 --> 00:31:43.020
It's not money.

00:31:43.020 --> 00:31:44.220
You know there's some people that think that.

00:31:44.220 --> 00:31:46.100
In fact, there have been studies that have been done

00:31:46.100 --> 00:31:48.980
that people have said this and the question has been

00:31:48.980 --> 00:31:52.020
how much more would make you happy?

00:31:53.020 --> 00:31:57.500
And you know in every income bracket of those

00:31:57.500 --> 00:32:00.820
that were surveyed in this particular survey,

00:32:00.820 --> 00:32:04.300
every single income bracket from the lowest to the highest

00:32:04.300 --> 00:32:06.220
of all those that were surveyed said,

00:32:06.220 --> 00:32:09.180
you know if I could just have about 15,000 more.

00:32:12.820 --> 00:32:15.420
Our greatest need is not finances.

00:32:15.420 --> 00:32:18.800
Our greatest need as humans is redemption.

00:32:19.800 --> 00:32:24.800
And our redemption cannot be paid for with finances.

00:32:25.680 --> 00:32:28.240
It can't be paid for with silver and gold.

00:32:28.240 --> 00:32:31.200
It can't be paid for with your works or my works.

00:32:31.200 --> 00:32:35.000
No, redemption is through the precious blood of Christ.

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:37.360
And the Bible teaches us that our greatest need

00:32:37.360 --> 00:32:38.680
and we're gonna look at it in a few minutes

00:32:38.680 --> 00:32:39.800
at the end of the text,

00:32:39.800 --> 00:32:43.120
but the reality is that your greatest need here this morning

00:32:43.120 --> 00:32:45.640
