00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:48.000
because he loved you and he rose again

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:50.760
paying for your sin and for the sin of the world

00:32:50.760 --> 00:32:52.680
and he desires to save you.

00:32:52.680 --> 00:32:53.960
That's the greatest need.

00:32:53.960 --> 00:32:56.400
But we begin to see the provision.

00:32:57.640 --> 00:32:59.600
He's my father.

00:32:59.600 --> 00:33:02.640
God has blessed Holly and I with having three children

00:33:02.640 --> 00:33:04.060
