00:33:05.560 --> 00:33:08.440
But you know as a human father

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:10.400
and those of you that have children,

00:33:10.400 --> 00:33:15.400
you know the way of desiring to provide for your children.

00:33:16.200 --> 00:33:19.220
Now, you know physically, humanly speaking,

00:33:19.220 --> 00:33:21.860
that your ability to provide for them is limited

00:33:21.860 --> 00:33:23.960
because you're limited and I'm limited.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.800
And we must depend upon God

00:33:26.800 --> 00:33:29.640
that we would provide for our children, our family,

00:33:29.640 --> 00:33:31.960
but we understand this morning that our God,

00:33:31.960 --> 00:33:36.400
our heavenly father, he has no limits

00:33:37.440 --> 00:33:39.200
and he can provide for you.

00:33:40.480 --> 00:33:42.920
Do you remember the account of Elijah?

