I know that ravens and crows aren't exactly the same,

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:55.200
but we got a bunch of crows around this property

00:33:55.200 --> 00:33:57.200
that I'd like to get rid of.

00:33:57.200 --> 00:33:59.540
Drive me absolutely insane.

00:34:00.940 --> 00:34:04.840
But God used a raven to feed his servant.

00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:06.600
Isn't that amazing?

00:34:06.600 --> 00:34:08.160
God is able.

00:34:08.160 --> 00:34:09.200
God's provision.

00:34:09.200 --> 00:34:11.020
I want you to notice not only God's provision,

00:34:11.060 --> 00:34:14.500
but in verses 11, and I know I read verse 11 there

00:34:14.500 --> 00:34:16.480
a moment ago, but 11 through 13,

00:34:16.480 --> 00:34:19.340
we see that as others are helped through the giving,

00:34:19.340 --> 00:34:23.020
