Think about our missionaries.

00:35:35.660 --> 00:35:38.020
So often we have opportunity to be able to give,

00:35:38.020 --> 00:35:41.100
yes, regularly to them each month,

00:35:41.100 --> 00:35:43.540
through our support of these missionaries

00:35:43.540 --> 00:35:46.620
