Because God's economy is not like our economy.

00:36:08.820 --> 00:36:11.380
God has the ability to move in the heart,

00:36:11.380 --> 00:36:14.420
in the life of someone in Northern Virginia,

00:36:14.420 --> 00:36:18.060
to give finances so that someone on a mission field,

00:36:18.060 --> 00:36:21.060
