00:36:25.580 --> 00:36:28.540
It's amazing how God works.

00:36:28.540 --> 00:36:30.380
And what happens?

00:36:30.380 --> 00:36:31.860
They praise God.

00:36:32.860 --> 00:36:35.220
They praise God.

00:36:35.220 --> 00:36:37.380
